of the Heritage Towpath Trail
on the Lichfield Canal"Ę
┤Kathleen Bird 
100 yrs.
So many memories with still more to come
Sit here and enjoy the little things in life
because one day you'll look back and realise
they were the big things."╝
╣"GONE BUT NEVER FORGOTTEN.
In loving memory of Dad, Mom and Sister.
Roy and Sylvia Cope and their youngest daughter
Mandy Jayne Lander.
Wherever you are ŌĆō I will always love you. Sue""▄
